                        <div class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-4 py-1 rounded-full font-bold">Days 31-60</div>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold">Scale & Optimize</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
                        <div class="flex gap-3">
                            <div class="text-blue-600 font-bold">Week 5-6:</div>
                            <div>Expand to 10 additional clients. Build Tableau Prep flows for remaining data format variations.
                            Optimize AI field mapping with learnings from pilot.</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex gap-3">
                            <div class="text-blue-600 font-bold">Week 7:</div>
